phrases: Just what are you...?
Where is Yin?
You are not Yin.
Where is she?
I am...
No!
You are just an observation spirit!
Why do you say that?
You are the one who changed me.
The spirit?
It does not matter, does it?
Even if I am like this?
Hei.
Yin...
I am glad.
Where is this?
So you have come to.
You are...!
He saved us.
This way.
Stop!
Do not worry.
If we wanted to kill you, we would have already done so.
We just want to talk to you two.
Stay here.
Okay.
Come in.
What do you want?
Why did you save me?
We did not exactly come to save you.
We just did not want them, formerly of the Syndicate, to have that doll.
Formerly?
The Syndicate no longer exists.
They are nothing but a mob trying to take claim to all the scattered powers.
The threat to contractors is now gone,
thanks to Amber giving her life so that you could choose the third option.
It may be hard to believe, but there are many here like you and me on the run from the Syndicate.
This is the truth.
Why are they after Yin?
She is a doll evolving at an unusually fast pace.
There are those who wish to know the reason why, and it is not just them.
And that includes me.
And all the more reason to since it was predicted more than 50 years ago in books.
What do you mean?
According to the books, a woman will awaken and obtain the power to change the world.
And what they want is that power.
Why Yin?
You are as oblivious as ever.
There is one thing I want to ask you too.
What is that doll to you?
Forget it.
Amber might have seen this future too.
Whether you stay here or leave is up to you.
Yin.
Tell me.
What is happening to you right now?
I do not know.
Something is trying to talk to me.
Something?
Your spirit?
Not exactly.
Is it possible for me to talk to it?
Not now.
Is there anything I can do?
Yin.
When it feels that you are near me, it begins to talk to me.
All you can do is leave me.
Let us split up.
If my being with you is hurting you,
there is nothing we can do but leave each other.
No.
Even if we split up,
I will not be able to forget about you.
That child was born from contractors.
Whether it is a blessing or not, it does not have any powers.
It is a strange place.
Free from the binds of human society,
these contractors rationally came to an agreement,
and gave birth to the most unpredictable thing.
The leader here once called for the evolution of contractors.
Is this a result of that?
I was told the future of contractors lies here.
It is quite different from what I expected it would be, but it does not seem to be a lie.
We are new to this place too.
We were scouted from Hong Kong, just like you.
Nice to meet you.
Here you go!
Thanks.
Sorry...
What are you doing?
That is my question!
I almost got killed!
If she had not stopped them, I would have been dead already!
Sorry for getting you involved.
Hey, that is not like you.
Still, what is up with this place?
They all act like contractors!
They are.
Everyone?
That is right.
Contractors who believed in their future.
Stop?
Why?
Compared to Hong Kong, her mind is stable and she seems to be quite calm.
She is no doubt Izanami.
Just as I told you, the Syndicate is in a bad position,
and by stimulating another awakening, you will be able to fulfill the former leader's wish that they could not carry out.
What is there to hesitate about?
You seem to be misunderstanding something.
We fought with Amber so that contractors would not go extinct,
not to stand above humans and rule.
You will not be able to do anything if you are scared, Amagiri!
You are a real punk.
Amagiri is an idiot.
Yes, he is.
But you seem more like an idiot to me.
Me? An idiot?
How so?
What are you planning to do with the doll?
So, you are against it?
Now that we know that she is Izanami, we have orders to kill her.
I just cannot agree with that order.
If she awakens, the world will break down.
It is already broken as it is.
So you are saying it is okay to make it even worse?
I do not think it is.
I do not want to die yet.
Even if it breaks down, it does not mean that us contractors will die.
I do not know about humans though.
I do not know what you heard from the Madame, but she is human.
I only heard one thing from her.
We are humans that could not become dolls.
Basically, we are defects.
You are just trash, doll.
Can I talk to you?
Sure.
We have found out who the people in Hong Kong were dealing with.
It was a Japanese secret service agent, but we do not know their name or who they belong to.
And there are rumors that an agency will be formed in Japan that consists of contractors.
Whether they are related or not, I do not know.
They are probably after the doll too,
and from what I know, they have gotten hold of a lot of information.
I do not know how much longer this place will last.
Now would be our chance to strike.
Where is Amagiri?
He is not coming.
We are doing it with just us.
Did you see where the Black Grim Reaper is?
He is in the jungle now.
Doing what?
Were not you going to kill kim?
Why?
Why are you after me?
Because Amagiri said so.
You foiled our plans and killed Amber!
You are our enemy.
Yin!
Li...
What happened?
I do not know!
I was sleeping, and then I heard a loud cry!
I was scared, so I was hiding the whole time!
And when it quieted down, I came out and did not see anyone!
Wait!
What the heck happened?
It is a baby.
Li!
What are you doing?
The baby is still crying!
According to the book, she will awaken and obtain the power to change the world.
Something tries to talk to me.
Something?
I am sorry!
I am sorry!
There, there.
That idiot got me.
What happened?
It was the young contractor that was with me.
He could not wait for your doll to awaken any longer.
He injected her with something and made her unstable.
I should have realized it sooner, but it was too late.
I tried to go warn you and this is what became of me.
I cannot stay in this dog any longer.
From what I saw, he was holding on to something,
and took your doll.
Where is she?
She is being followed.
Your doll has not completely awakened yet.
In the end, she stopped the awakening herself.
You can still make it.
So...
Go kill her already.
Can you fly?
ano sora ni kagayaku Ziggy Star
Can you fly?
Ziggy Star shining in the sky
kowareta yume kieta ai torimodoshite Fly away
Claiming back my broken dreams and lost love Fly away
Can you try?
nikushimi o jihi e to kaete
Can you try?
Changing this hate into compassion
kawaita mune o nurasu Darker than Black
Soaking up my dry chest Darker than Black
utsuro ni hikaru kousou no mado
From hollow spaces the windows on the skyscrapers shine,
hatasenu mama no yakusoku
a promise that remains unfulfilled
muda ni nagareta chi to namida ni somaru kanashii Game
Dyed in pointlessly flowing blood and tears, this sad Game
Oh, Where is my friend?
hitori yozora o nagamereba
Oh, Where is my friend?
If I Gaze at the night sky alone
hoshikage ni yureru kimi no Sweet smile
Swaying in the starlight is your Sweet smile
Can you try?
tachihadakaru kabe o kowashite
Can you try?
Break the wall that is blocking your way
tabidatsu toki o kizamu Darker than Black
The time to begin is ticking by Darker than Black
The battle continues, and the ruins are smeared in blood.
Are they after evolution or destruction?
Why was Yin chosen?
She slips through my held out hands, and falls.
